CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1949, pg. 24 reads: "Trapshoot Winners - The first annual Pittsburgh Courier Trapshoot was won by the Ocoee Rifle Club on June 19 at the North Park Range. Shown above are the winners: L. Devereaux, W.M. Robinson, Christey Wilkey, Henry Devereaux and Thomas Devereaux. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Ocoee Rifle Club members L. Devereaux, W. M. Robinson, Christey Wilkey, Henry Devereaux, and Thomas Devereaux, posed holding rifles in Harris Studio
